{"tid":1716300,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"〈突發．求聽推到上熱門〉最新抗爭歌曲〈港殤〉 －  記11232019香港","createTime":"2019-11-13T10:06:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T14:02:11.000Z","uid":117737,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f53f870e76f464661957432d227db9cd69d90c32","tid":1716300,"uid":117737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T10:06:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">我知道大家撐到呢一刻，真是非常之支力，心力交瘁。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n作左首歌，想送俾每一位起呢一刻，仍然努力為自己理想堅持的香港人。<br />\n<br />\n起想屌任何人<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「唔好再唱歌啦打緊杖呀！」</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之前，我想同大家講，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>除左食物之外，我地都極需要精神食糧去重振人心、振奮士氣－除左食物同急救之外，我地仲需要堅強既意志去打呢場杖！！！！唔係淨是生理上！！我地心靈上都需要巨大的意志同堅持！！</strong></span></span>但願任何一個香港人、不論勇武定和理非，<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>聽完都能重獲堅持的力量！！去回想番我地堅持既心！！花5分鐘就好！！我希望呢首歌能讓大家重獲呢種堅持既勇氣！！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>我要大家煲底再見呀！！！唔要遺書呀做乜撚野呀！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n我唔識專業錄音／編曲／混音，只能盡最大能力整左段片彈同唱；錄得唔好、唱得唔完美，希望唔好介意。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/XHu5czbGnIs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FXHu5czbGnIs&d=eC9RRsiBNQJpYHZqEQI0QkbB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=7e108802\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/XHu5czbGnIs</a><br />\n<br />\n歌譜下載： <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=1qhnIJnkJhdCYBKrDFRKIWFTXp9yqs-u2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D1qhnIJnkJhdCYBKrDFRKIWFTXp9yqs-u2&d=eC9RRsiBNQJpYHZqEQI0QkbB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=4769e212\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=1qhnIJnkJhdCYBKrDFRKIWFTXp9yqs-u2</a><br />\n<br />\n聲明：<br />\n- 歌曲版權屬本人所有，歡迎任何人聯絡／通知我，為歌曲進行後製<br />\n- 歌譜開放讓任何人下載<br />\n<br />\n〔港殤〕<br />\n發誓 齊集煲底裡 慶祝<br />\n你 我終可現實裡相擁<br />\n發夢 時日多久也記得<br />\n願榮光歸香港<br />\n<br />\n萬人汗 萬人淚 港殤<br />\n在談論如何彌補這創傷<br />\n怎也不會 磨滅心中的理想（忘掉初心的理想）<br />\n槍炮中萬人亦再唱<br />\n即便跌倒仍要起身再上 相信<br />\n終可激起萬尺光芒<br />\n榮光歸於這裡<br />\n<br />\n發誓 來日煲底裡 慶祝<br />\n你 我終可熱淚裡相擁<br />\n記住 魂斷歸天國手足<br />\n誓要 榮光歸香港<br />\n<br />\n大家歸家再唱<br />\n<br />\n#光復香港時代革命 #抗暴之戰<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"90d8e86718e37cb16af7f078bb2944619a06b4f0","tid":1716300,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T10:10:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">連登冷氣軍師 rt like reply</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">你哋已經唔使上前線搏命，係咪連呢啲都做唔到？</span><br />\n最新<br />\n<br />\n！！！！Sen. Cory Gardner (Colorado)<br />\n關注中大 支持香港<br />\n！！！！佢未cosponsor條Act 請佢幫忙！！！！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenCoryGardner/status/1194341990655246346?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenCoryGardner%2Fstatus%2F1194341990655246346%3Fs%3D19&d=eC9RRsiBNQJpYHZqEQI0QkbB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=c177f9c3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenCoryGardner%2Fstatus%2F1194341990655246346%3Fs%3D19&h=c0f128d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenCoryGardner/status/1194341990655246346?s=1